WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:06.101
Hey, good morning family. I have another video for you all today.

00:00:06.102 --> 00:00:13.082
I've been praying early this morning and seeking Him about what to do for a video for you all.

00:00:13.083 --> 00:00:22.596
When I was praying, the Lord showed me more about what's coming.

00:00:22.597 --> 00:00:40.786
I was going to deliver a lot of this word to you and tell you about more preparation, but when I was at the sink doing the dishes again tonight, the Lord spoke to me and He said, 'Brandon, they need a foundation. They're going to have to have a foundation of the Word.

00:00:40.787 --> 00:00:58.008
You can keep delivering the word and telling them what's coming, son, but I'm warning you to pray over this stuff.'This is what I'm trying to tell you: the gross darkness that's coming and the things that would be like throwing gas on the fire for you all.

00:00:58.009 --> 00:01:15.153
I know people are curious about what's coming, and it's important to know, but it's more important for you to have a foundation of the Word and know how to stand on it for what's coming than anything else.

00:01:15.154 --> 00:01:37.002
You can know what's coming and be totally destroyed, or you can have a foundation of the Word of God and be able to resist, stand fast, and know how to believe for things to have victory in this storm.

00:01:37.003 --> 00:02:01.631
If you don't have the Word and a concrete foundation—not a sandy soil or quicksand foundation—we're going to have a Word-based foundation of solid rock so that you can build your house on it and the storms of life will not blow down your home.

00:02:01.632 --> 00:02:14.298
But if you do not have a foundation in the Word and it's on sand, your house is going to be swept away when the wave comes.

00:02:14.299 --> 00:02:17.824
We'll get to all that stuff later; it's not important right now.

00:02:17.825 --> 00:02:26.434
What's important is for you to understand: have you sat at the feet of Jesus today?

00:02:26.435 --> 00:02:36.623
Have you sat with Him and started to develop a relationship with the Father sitting at His feet?

00:02:36.624 --> 00:02:48.011
It is so important that you take the time every day to get in the Word and read your Bible.

00:02:48.012 --> 00:02:53.319
Find scriptures that pertain to what you're believing for.

00:02:53.320 --> 00:03:00.559
Like I've said over and over, start reading the New Testament all the way through.

00:03:00.560 --> 00:03:10.732
Read two and three chapters a day. Spend 20 to 30 minutes inside the Word.

00:03:10.733 --> 00:03:19.745
If you can spend 30 minutes on Facebook, Instagram, and YouTube watching these videos, you can take 20 minutes for the Word.

00:03:19.746 --> 00:03:27.842
I would rather you not watch any videos at all—mine or anyone else's on the prophetic network on YouTube—and take that time for the Word instead.

00:03:27.843 --> 00:03:34.420
If you say you don't have enough time, then don't watch my video; get in the Word.

00:03:34.421 --> 00:03:42.581
It's more important for you to get in the Word than to watch me or anybody else.

00:03:42.582 --> 00:04:01.342
The Word is the priority in your life, period. Pray. It has to be the priority for what's coming, or you will not make it.

00:04:01.343 --> 00:04:08.620
I'm just telling you, that may sound scary, but it needs to scare you because gross darkness is coming.

00:04:08.621 --> 00:04:14.958
Very dark times are coming for the world, though not for the body of Christ.

00:04:14.959 --> 00:04:39.975
Just like it says in Isaiah: 'Arise, shine, for thy light is come, and the glory of the Lord is risen upon thee.'The rest of the verse talks about great darkness on the earth because of sin and gross darkness on the people.

00:04:39.976 --> 00:04:53.253
If there's really bad darkness on these people and you're the light, how are you going to stay in the light? Have you sat at the feet of Jesus today?

00:04:53.254 --> 00:05:02.037
Have you listened to Him and talked to Him about your life, your direction, and where you're supposed to be living?

00:05:02.038 --> 00:05:09.728
Are you living in a high-rise in New York City while God is trying to tell you to live in the country?

00:05:09.729 --> 00:05:13.577
Are you in downtown Chicago and God is saying you need to move?

00:05:13.578 --> 00:05:20.036
You might have a good job, but you're not seeking Him on another job while He's trying to tell you to move.

00:05:20.037 --> 00:05:24.411
I'm telling you, you need to be in the place that God has for you.

00:05:24.412 --> 00:05:30.630
Maybe He wants you in those cities because you're going to be a light there, but maybe He's trying to tell you to do something else.

00:05:30.631 --> 00:05:35.928
You just need to hear Him. People say they don't hear His voice at all; it's because you're not in the Word.

00:05:35.929 --> 00:05:54.840
I was listening to statistics from Pastor Steve, who said 97% of all Christians don't read their Bible on a daily basis and only 3% have read the Word all the way through.

00:05:54.841 --> 00:06:05.500
When I heard that statistic at church, I thought, 'This is serious.'The foundation of the Word is what's going to get you through hard times.

00:06:05.501 --> 00:06:16.865
You have got to get that Bible out and read it. If you say it's too hard to understand, get a translation that you do understand.

00:06:16.866 --> 00:06:35.761
It may be the New Living Translation—there are all kinds of really good translations.

00:06:35.762 --> 00:06:44.069
Let's not get religious about this. If you don't understand the King James Version, find a Bible that ministers to you.

00:06:44.070 --> 00:06:58.271
If you're a teenager and you can only understand something like The Message Bible, that's better than nothing.

00:06:58.272 --> 00:07:29.270
Read the Word. It may be modernized, but it's the Word of God and it's going to change your life.

00:07:29.271 --> 00:07:48.362
The Amplified Bible is also a good version that will help you.

00:07:48.363 --> 00:07:56.519
I read all kinds of different translations because everything ministers to me differently.

00:07:56.520 --> 00:08:14.138
Let's just get in the Word and not be petty. Read two or three chapters every day.

00:08:14.139 --> 00:08:30.195
When I talk about practicing the presence of the Lord, I'm talking about visualizing Him being there with you.

00:08:30.196 --> 00:08:37.219
Talk to Him like you'd talk to your son or daughter. Visualize that Jesus Christ is living on the inside of you.

00:08:37.220 --> 00:08:48.817
I'm not saying to pretend; Jesus is real and He is living on the inside of you.

00:08:48.817 --> 00:09:03.347
You practice His presence by thinking, 'Jesus, how is Your day today?'Visualize Him sitting there with you.

00:09:03.348 --> 00:09:11.048
Think about it in your head: Jesus is in me, He is with me, and I'm going to practice talking to Him. Don't act like He's far away.

00:09:11.049 --> 00:09:18.708
He said, 'I'll never leave you nor forsake you; lo, I am with you always, even unto the end of the world.'That means He is dwelling in you.

00:09:18.709 --> 00:09:30.929
The very atmosphere can get charged with the power of the Holy Ghost if you start worshiping and meditating on His Word.

00:09:30.930 --> 00:09:48.037
Lord, I want to know You more; teach me Your ways. The Bible says His sheep will know His voice, and a stranger's voice they will not follow.

00:09:48.038 --> 00:10:00.775
How do you know someone's voice? You become familiar with them.

00:10:00.776 --> 00:10:26.648
If my wife calls me, I know her voice immediately. If my son calls, I know immediately it's him.

00:10:26.649 --> 00:10:42.885
Why? Because you've spent time with them and developed a relationship over years.

00:10:42.886 --> 00:10:52.702
It's the same way you develop a relationship with the Lord; you spend time with Him.

00:10:52.703 --> 00:11:15.694
The more time you spend in prayer and reading His Word, the more you're going to know His voice.

00:11:15.695 --> 00:11:34.697
For instance, my grandfather was one of my best friends. I knew his voice perfectly, but he passed away 12 years ago.

00:11:34.698 --> 00:11:41.031
I began to forget how his voice sounded until I found an old video recording of him.

00:11:41.032 --> 00:12:04.294
I heard his voice and started crying because it was so precious to me. Once you go back to it, you don't forget it again.

00:12:04.295 --> 00:12:14.892
But if you don't spend quality time with that voice, you start to forget the pitch.

00:12:14.893 --> 00:13:02.597
You've got to read the Bible and pray. Let's make a plan to get in the Word every day.

00:13:02.598 --> 00:13:10.553
We can start it now for the Jewish New Year; let's do it in Rosh Hashanah. We don't have to wait for January.

00:13:10.554 --> 00:13:38.799
If you feed your flesh three times a day, but your spirit is starving, you're in trouble.

00:13:38.800 --> 00:13:50.499
Most people only feed their spirit for 30 minutes on Sunday.

00:13:50.500 --> 00:14:06.495
If you go to a mega church and the only Bible time you have is reading scriptures on the teleprompter, that's not enough.

00:14:06.496 --> 00:14:33.222
Your spirit needs to eat in the morning and at night. If you start feeding your spirit, your life is going to change because God is the Word.

00:14:33.223 --> 00:14:45.108
He inspired those words; they are Him, and they bring life into you.

00:14:45.109 --> 00:14:50.682
It's like taking a spiritual bath every time you get in that Bible.

00:14:50.683 --> 00:15:16.876
Renew your mind in it. Pray and take a big spiritual drink. If you do this, it will change your life.

00:15:16.877 --> 00:15:21.581
If you don't hear the voice of God, it's because you're not spending time with Him.

00:15:21.582 --> 00:15:26.872
He is no respecter of persons. If He talks to me, He will talk to you.

00:15:26.873 --> 00:15:41.640
My 8-year-old daughter hears the voice of the Lord because I'm teaching her at a young age.

00:15:41.641 --> 00:16:01.013
He didn't make it hard; you just get in the Word, pray, and meditate on it.

00:16:01.014 --> 00:16:08.416
This is not something you do once; it's something you do every day.

00:16:08.417 --> 00:16:16.477
There are 365 days a year, 24 hours in a day, 52 weeks in a year.

00:16:16.478 --> 00:16:32.638
This is your staple, just like eating and breathing. Read your Bible every day, period.

00:16:32.639 --> 00:16:43.612
By this time next year, right before the presidential elections in America, you will look back and remember what I told you.

00:16:43.613 --> 00:16:49.074
You will say, 'My life has forever changed.'I challenge you to a year of this.

00:16:49.075 --> 00:17:23.913
You don't go to the gym just once to lose weight; you have to go to the spiritual gym.

00:17:23.914 --> 00:17:29.600
Eat the Word and meditate on it. Lift those spiritual weights.

00:17:29.601 --> 00:18:00.207
In a year—or even 30 days—see where you are spiritually. I give you a 30-day challenge starting right now.

00:18:00.208 --> 00:18:23.931
Where will you be on October 6th? Start now, reading three or four chapters and meditating on a verse that stands out to you.

00:18:23.932 --> 00:18:57.437
Memorize it. 'The grass withers and the flower fades, but the word of the Lord remains forever.'Get that inside your soul.

00:18:57.438 --> 00:19:27.811
Memorize First Peter, memorize Isaiah, and know that 'Greater is He that is in you than he that is in the world.'Know Second Timothy 1:7: 'God has not given you a spirit of fear, but of power, and of love, and of a sound mind.'You need those scriptures for what's coming.

00:19:27.812 --> 00:19:37.649
When the devourer comes knocking at your door, it's too late to start reading.

00:19:37.650 --> 00:19:55.295
You can't say, 'Hold on, Mr. Devil, I've got to get in my Bible for a bit.'He’s already there.

00:19:55.296 --> 00:20:07.312
You have to submit yourself unto God, resist the devil, and he will flee.

00:20:07.313 --> 00:20:32.957
You need to know that He's made you more than a conqueror through Christ Jesus.

00:20:32.958 --> 00:20:57.139
Your mountain has to hear your voice—the power of God in your voice. Faith calls those things that be not as though they were.

00:20:57.140 --> 00:21:06.018
It doesn't do any good to know what's coming if you don't have a foundation in the Word, because the winds and waves of life are coming.

00:21:06.019 --> 00:21:14.448
You better have a revelation of who He is so you can understand your covenant.

00:21:14.449 --> 00:21:35.734
It's time to get a foundation so that you can stand on the Word and know that you have not seen the righteous forsaken nor his seed begging bread.

00:21:35.735 --> 00:21:57.288
If He takes care of the sparrow, He will take care of you. If He multiplied for the five thousand, and if He provided for the widow with Elijah, He'll provide for you.

00:21:57.289 --> 00:22:16.734
We've got to get in the Word so you can hear Him. Father, I just thank You right now in the name of Jesus for my brothers and sisters.

00:22:16.735 --> 00:22:28.341
I lift them up before You and thank You for the blood of Jesus Christ that covers them from head to toe.

00:22:28.342 --> 00:22:52.202
We take authority over the spirit of fear, torment, depression, and anxiety.

00:22:52.203 --> 00:23:29.239
We cast our cares upon You, for we know You care for us. You loved us enough to send Your Son to die for us, so You will provide for us.

00:23:29.240 --> 00:23:40.853
Father, help these people have a hunger for a revelation of Your Word.

00:23:40.854 --> 00:23:46.752
I plead the blood over their ears that they have spiritual ears to hear what the Spirit is saying.

00:23:46.753 --> 00:23:55.674
Holy Spirit, I thank You that You're stirring in them and getting them excited about Your Word.

00:23:55.675 --> 00:24:15.297
I pray that the eyes of their understanding would be enlightened, according to Ephesians, and flooded with light today.

00:24:15.298 --> 00:24:25.359
I plead the blood over their minds, their wills, and their emotions.

00:24:25.360 --> 00:24:53.723
Give them wisdom like Solomon. No torment comes nigh them. Father, I thank You that as they seek You, they will find You.

00:24:53.724 --> 00:24:59.719
I thank You that Your presence is filling their house right now.

00:24:59.720 --> 00:25:31.109
Show them how much You love them and give them the peace that passes understanding.

00:25:31.110 --> 00:25:49.491
I thank You that You meet their needs—spiritually, physically, financially, and emotionally.

00:25:49.492 --> 00:26:21.003
I come in agreement for their finances and for healing. By Your stripes, we are healed.

00:26:21.004 --> 00:26:29.622
You were wounded for our transgressions and bruised for our iniquities.

00:26:29.623 --> 00:26:50.359
We sit at Your feet today and ask, 'Lord, what's on Your heart today?'We put You first.

00:26:50.360 --> 00:27:09.678
We breathe in those pages; we breathe You in, Father. We drink from the well.

00:27:09.679 --> 00:27:38.799
Lord, we're thirsty for a mighty move of God. Pour out Your Holy Ghost; I want to see the hand of God move mightily.

00:27:38.800 --> 00:29:44.222
I'm hungry for a move of God. Fill my cup, Lord; I lift it up. Come and quench this thirsting of my soul.

00:29:44.223 --> 00:32:01.914
Bread of Heaven, feed me till I want no more. Fill my cup, fill it up, and make me whole.

00:32:01.915 --> 00:32:20.185
He inhabits the praises of His people. If you enter His courts with praise, the manifestation of His glory comes.

00:32:20.186 --> 00:33:01.094
When praises go up, blessings come down. Worship Him first with thanksgiving. Thank Him for what you have.

00:33:01.095 --> 00:36:27.951
Don't go in like a spoiled brat acting like He owes you; He's already done it all. Even if I'm just dust, I refuse to let a rock do my job.

00:36:27.952 --> 00:36:43.878
Let everything that has breath praise the Lord, for He is worthy regardless of your circumstances.

00:36:43.879 --> 00:37:28.615
Get in that place of worship right now. Even if you only have a cracker to eat, be thankful and watch Him move on your behalf.

00:37:28.616 --> 00:37:55.630
I remember when my parents had no money and no food. We were hungry, staying in a hotel with cockroaches, and Dad had no job.

00:37:55.631 --> 00:38:33.962
Mom pulled all the coins out of her purse just to get some cheap tacos.

00:38:33.963 --> 00:39:14.820
My sister went back to that coin purse, praying, and found a supernatural $20 bill in there.

00:39:14.821 --> 00:39:38.651
We rejoiced because we got to eat! God comes through. He's been faithful to me when I've had nothing.

00:39:38.652 --> 00:40:06.049
Don't give up. You've got to learn how to believe by faith. God's going to do an accelerated time for you because Jesus is coming.

00:40:06.050 --> 00:40:25.782
I bless you all in the mighty name of Jesus. I believe for healing and prosperity for you.

00:40:25.783 --> 00:40:33.904
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart. Jesus loves you, and we love you.

00:40:33.905 --> 00:40:44.079
We will see you next time. Have a blessed and wonderful day. Bye-bye.

